  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GEF GOLD+ in Madagascar: Enhancing the formalization and mercury reduction in artisanal and small-scale gold mining in Madagascar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Child project part of the GOLD+ programme on artisanal gold mining under the leadership of Conservation International and with funding from the GEF. The project was developed at the request received by the UNIDO Country Office in late August 2019 from the GEF OFP that followed the completion of the National Action Plan on the artisanal and small-scale gold mining sector (an obligation under the Minamata Convention).</narrative>
